attributes.title: This app just doesn’t work right :(
attributes.review: I downloaded this app so I could so I could keep up with the Trump campaign but unfortunately it’s just way too unresponsive and drains your battery life like no other. I tried to donate $10 but the donate widget added two extra zeros!!!! DISAPPOINTED

attributes.title: Don’t download this app.
attributes.review: Hi so I downloaded this app and I’m extremely disappointed. I got a virus. Every time I open an app a Cheeto appears on my screen🤮. How am I supposed to live. My cat took a look at the Cheeto and ran. We are still looking for whiskers. To who ever made this app I don’t like you. My cat is dead because of you. I don’t want Cheetos on my screen. Or an orange crayon. Screw make America great again. Bring my cat home again 2020.

attributes.title: HUGE disappointment:(((
attributes.review: I was SO EXCITED to download this app but then it took two whole hours to download (even though i have plenty of storage and good wifi connection), and then even once I opened the app it wouldn’t connect to wifi! Honestly an embarrassment for the entire campaign, can’t believe they let these issues occur! So sad:(( Also I think it gave my phone a virus???
